beautiful calculations,

00:12:58.110 --> 00:13:02.340 align:middle line:84%
and enhanced our understanding
of non-living systems.

00:13:02.340 --> 00:13:04.640 align:middle line:84%
Descartes really looked
at the world as a machine.

00:13:04.640 --> 00:13:07.410 align:middle line:84%
