mechanistic universe

00:13:34.140 --> 00:13:38.340 align:middle line:84%
that is conceived of
as gears and knobs

00:13:38.340 --> 00:13:40.530 align:middle line:90%
sort of linking together.

00:13:40.530 --> 00:13:44.470 align:middle line:84%
That is going to change because
