00:13:44.470 --> 00:13:47.520 align:middle line:84%
We know from a physics
point of view it's not true.

00:13:47.520 --> 00:13:50.790 align:middle line:84%
The impact of that change
is still somewhat difficult

00:13:50.790 --> 00:13:53.790 align:middle line:84%
to guess, but one
of the areas that I

00:13:53.790 --> 00:13:55.800 align:middle line:84%
know is going to
make a big impact

00:13:55.800 --> 00:13:59.680 align:middle line:84%
is in how we understand the
nature of human experience,

00:13:59.680 --> 00:14:03.820 align:middle line:84%
because human experience in a
clockwork world doesn't fit.

00:14:03.820 --> 00:14:07.640 align:middle line:84%
And that's why in mainstream
psychology for many years

00:14:07.640 --> 00:14:10.240 align:middle line:84%
