internal experience

00:14:10.240 --> 00:14:12.490 align:middle line:90%
was considered to be laughable.

00:14:12.490 --> 00:14:14.290 align:middle line:84%
There was no
internal experience.

00:14:14.290 --> 00:14:16.000 align:middle line:90%
