00:14:16.000 --> 00:14:17.560 align:middle line:84%
And the reason it
was explained away

00:14:17.560 --> 00:14:21.370 align:middle line:84%
is because of this idea of
living in a clockwork world.

00:14:21.370 --> 00:14:25.060 align:middle line:84%
>> Darwin countered the
